01:00.661 --> 01:04.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And now it's laid out the
punishment, targeting
key leaders and agencies in
Moscow.

01:04.998 --> 01:09.102 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The word came from Hawaii, where
the president
is vacationing.

01:09.136 --> 01:11.305 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
