attribution to
the highest levels of the
Russian government.

06:51.911 --> 06:55.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was done in the statement
from the DNI
and from the secretary of
homeland security

06:55.915 --> 07:00.353 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
