level of the
president.

07:12.499 --> 07:17.370 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And these actions also follow
extensive outreach
to state and local governments
to shore up

07:17.404 --> 07:22.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
