really, really try
to make you proud.

50:20.851 --> 50:28.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KENYA DOWNS: By being a hand or
a model for
some other young woman who one
day may see

50:28.559 --> 50:34.598 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
me, may see a woman who looks
like me and
like you, and know that she can,
too.

50:34.632 --> 50:38.435 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TANZINA VEGA: Thank you from the
bottom of
my heart.

50:38.469 --> 50:40.371 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JASMINE WRIGHT: Thank you, Gwen.

