that research
I lost my right eye to ocular
melanoma.

51:02.793 --> 51:06.931 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So, you're a
cancer researcher
working at the NIH, and you lose
your right

51:06.964 --> 51:08.132 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
